# Neo Card™ Demo Backend – AEI Secure Lite Version

## Environment Configuration

### Local Development
- Database: SQLite
- Port: 3000
- Environment: development

### Production (Render)
- Database: SQLite (or PostgreSQL if needed)
- Port: Dynamic (Render assigned)
- Environment: production

## Environment Variables

```bash
# Server Configuration
NODE_ENV=development
PORT=3000

# Database Configuration
DB_PATH=./database/neocard.db

# Security Configuration
JWT_SECRET=your-super-secret-jwt-key-here
AEI_SECRET_KEY=your-aei-secret-key-for-hmac
API_KEY_SECRET=your-api-key-secret

# Anti-fraud Configuration
COOLDOWN_MINUTES=5
DAILY_SCAN_LIMIT=100

# CORS Configuration
CORS_ORIGIN=http://localhost:3000

# Rate Limiting
RATE_LIMIT_WINDOW_MS=900000
RATE_LIMIT_MAX_REQUESTS=100
```

## Installation

```bash
npm install
```

## Development

```bash
npm run dev
```

## Production

```bash
npm start
```

## Testing

```bash
npm test
```
